Class MenuItemInstance

java.lang.Object
  org.dmd.features.extgwt.client.util.menu.MenuItemInstance
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultMenuItem, DefaultToolbarItem
public abstract class MenuItemInstance
extends java.lang.Object
implements MenuSubItemIF, TriggerIF

The MenuItemInstance class provides a common base for menu items that represent actual trigger points for functionality, as opposed to submenus.
